title: Prabowo Subianto | Biography, Career, & Facts | Britannica
snippet: Prabowo Subianto is a former Indonesian army general and businessman, born on October 17, 1951, in Jakarta.

title: Prabowo Subianto - Wikipedia
snippet: Prabowo Subianto Djojohadikusumo (born 17 October 1951) is an Indonesian politician, businessman, and retired military officer who has served as the eighth president of Indonesia since 2024. He previously served as the 26th minister of defense under President Joko Widodo from 2019 to 2024.

title: Candidate profile: Prabowo Subianto - Runners and Riders - The Jakarta Post
snippet: Prabowo Subianto Djojohadikusumo, 72, is a retired Army lieutenant general, a businessman and the incumbent Defense Minister (2019-present). Due to his proximity to power throughout his military career, he entered politics in 2004 to pursue his dream of becoming the nations president.
